1. Change the path variables in run.py accordingly.

2. Make MD inputs (you can increase the number of trajectories if you want.)
$ python input_gen.py -d ../../TUT1/02-dftb-BOMD-psb3/sampling/ -f run.py -n 200

3. Execute the dynamics
$ python submit_all.py

4. Do a statistical analysis with statistical_analysis.py 
$ python statistical_analysis.py -n 5 -s 600 -t 2
